From yesterday @stissinghouse . A huge thank you to @deborahneedleman ,  @clare.deboer and @saltycitrus for orchestrating such a magical event. Thank you to everyone who came out and to everyone who brought home a collage or photograph. It was so special to see my pieces head out into the world and to meet so many incredible new people. And special thank you to @mushloostu for all of your help and for being by my side all day. Thank you! ✨ 

P.s- There are 3 framed collages from this collection that are still available. If interested, please send a message to studio@arieldearieflowers.com ❤️

Collage on Arches paper in an antique frame

All of the collages from this first collection have officially sold! Thank you to everyone who expressed interest. I loved seeing them find their new homes and am excited to start work on a new collection for Spring. Stay tuned! 🌸
